Lizzie Cundy looked the epitome of glam as she posed up a storm in a series of stunning snaps. The star, 54, donned a dazzling evening gown as she documented behind-the-scenes goings-on for the shoot of a new tanning range in view of her 68,000 followers. Lizzie looked phenomenal as she flashed side boob in the satin dress. She also showcased her enviably toned legs thanks to the daring nature of the garment. In another shot, Lizzie wore a high-leg white swimsuit with a fringed jacket draped over the shoulders.